Joan Collins, 89, took to Instagram to share a heartfelt message and an array of pictures to mark her daughter Katy's, birthday. The actress looked beyond glamorous in the unearthed snaps with her daughter Katyana. She captioned the post in view of her 278,000 Instagram followers: "Happy Birthday to my favorite fellow Gemini, my beautiful daughter Katy! #birthday #gemini #daughter #love." Joan had Katyana in 1972 with her husband at the time, American businessman Ron Kass. The award-winning actress also has Tara and Alexander from her marriage to the late Anthony Newley.